CS TECHNICAL OFFICER: Coalition technology and engineering officer

A Coalition officer specializing in advanced technology, cybernetics,
and field engineering. Technical Officers are the technical backbone of
CS operations, keeping power armor, weapons, and communications running
in the field.

STARTING PACKAGE
  Skills: Computer operation, computer programming, basic electronics,
    advanced electronics, military etiquette, radio basic, W.P. energy
    pistol, plus elective picks from Technical, Science, Electrical,
    Mechanical, and Military categories.
  Attribute requirements: IQ 14.
  Equipment: CS officer uniform, portable tech kit, laptop computer,
    concealed sidearm, CS technical badge, and field engineering tools.
  Credits: 500 credits (standard kit).
  PPE / ISP: No starting PPE or ISP.

SEE ALSO: occs, classes, cs military specialist
